Package: plottwist2
Title: Handy Functions for ggplot2
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Joseph", "Pennycook", , "joe.pennycook@hotmail.co.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Several functions to speed up the creation of neat plots with ggplot2 or expand functionality. In particular, functions to allow a wider range of point shapes (symbols) or bar chart textures (patterns), reducing the reliance on colour to distinguish between groups.
